<p class="ql-align-center">历史不仅是 厚重 的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是 鲜活 的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每件文物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都是一段历史的见证</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有着鲜为人知的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200816/b28d9aa692594e80879e95692121b399.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> “故”土翻新“事” </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你准备好听故事了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天的讲述人是：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200816/22c3e0d005504b9f9be38c1817ec650c.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
